        }

## User Story [/user/{userName}/story/{storyId}]

### View a User's story [GET]

+ Parameters

    + userName: KFStreetArt (required, string) - Username of the user who created this story.
    + storyId: 1230dso (required, string) - ID for this story.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [Story]

# Data Structures

## Partial Story (object)
+ url (required)
+ title (string, required)
+ description (string, required)
+ visits (number, required)
+ location (array[number], required)
+ audioFiles
+ imageFiles
